1699
01:05:13,170 --> 01:05:16,190
for just to have something in your head.

1700
01:05:16,810 --> 01:05:18,890
One of them is rotation symmetry,

1701
01:05:19,970 --> 01:05:22,170
where it just says that if you take a system

1702
01:05:22,170 --> 01:05:23,850
which satisfies a certain set of equations,

1703
01:05:23,850 --> 01:05:25,710
and you rotate it,

1704
01:05:25,710 --> 01:05:26,910
physically rotate it,

1705
01:05:26,930 --> 01:05:28,510
physically rotate it about an axis,

1706
01:05:28,770 --> 01:05:30,510
you may or may not change it.

1707
01:05:30,630 --> 01:05:31,510
I can tell you this,

1708
01:05:31,510 --> 01:05:32,390
if you rotate me,

1709
01:05:32,570 --> 01:05:33,530
you'll change me.

1710
01:05:34,190 --> 01:05:35,010
You will.

1711
01:05:36,130 --> 01:05:38,050
If the Earth weren't here,

1712
01:05:38,170 --> 01:05:40,250
and I was in outer space and free space,

1713
01:05:41,750 --> 01:05:44,510
then the Lennard equation,

1714
01:05:44,950 --> 01:05:46,810
whatever the equation governing me is,

1715
01:05:46,990 --> 01:05:50,630
would be the same for the rotated or the unrotated.

1716
01:05:51,070 --> 01:05:53,170
Another way of saying it is I couldn't tell

1717
01:05:53,170 --> 01:05:54,810
whether I was rotated or not.

1718
01:05:54,930 --> 01:05:56,650
If you rotate me and then just go away,

1719
01:05:56,790 --> 01:05:58,090
